@baseUrl = https://backend-fieri.vercel.app/
@contentType = application/json

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### MODULE : ORGANIZATION (Routes Publiques)
### ------------------------------------------------------------

# @name getCountries
# Récupérer la liste de tous les pays
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

